{"tid":1937173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"意大利死亡率破9%增800死，西班牙大爆發，荷蘭比利時開始暴增期","createTime":"2020-03-21T17:32:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T04:49:17.000Z","uid":82002,"like":67,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"28dbceb38af3171d4770829f6e685374b25e69d6","tid":1937173,"uid":82002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T17:32:59.000Z","msg":"意大利死亡確診雙雙破紀錄，<br />\n單單倫巴底地區死亡六百人，<br />\n目前recovery 同 death 比率係可怕既1.5:1，<br />\n有報導指全國8%醫護已被感染。<br />\n<br />\n西班牙目前狀況大約係一星期前既意大利，<br />\n今日一日新增近4000確診300死，<br />\n死亡率上升到接近5%<br />\n不過佢地隔離做得比意大利好，<br />\n估計唔會有意大利咁嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n美國德國保持大約10%確診人數上升，<br />\n死亡率被控制得好好，<br />\n得益於兩國充足既醫療資源。<br />\n<br />\n荷蘭比利時新增確診20%，<br />\n死亡案例開始穩步上升，<br />\n目前大約係一個禮拜前既西班牙，<br />\n預料好快會開始爬升。<br />\n<br />\n巴基斯坦，盧森堡一日新增約30%確診，<br />\n值得繼續觀察。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/03/22/012534_9804c479dba44e86d0379fbd53649b38.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F03%2F22%2F012534_9804c479dba44e86d0379fbd53649b38.png&h=8a3d8fb9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f137128a574e53303cbc1f06a77a06c7156775ab","tid":1937173,"uid":162910,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T17:34:52.000Z","msg":"新黑死病"},{"pid":"e8e078c31baea3188bd09139bc938240d904b4f5","tid":1937173,"uid":82002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T17:35:16.000Z","msg":"疫情速報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e6101ae03361302e8af55df483bf94aa42df766","tid":1937173,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T17:37:22.000Z","msg":"死亡數字冇放緩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d55f0785e6f9e71084f1ac1c966c11178a63545","tid":1937173,"uid":82002,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"2e6101ae03361302e8af55df483bf94aa42df766","tid":1937173,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy